text: Andrew James Redmayne (born 13 January 1989) is an Australian soccer player. He plays as goalkeeper for Sydney FC in the A-League Men and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==Career statistics== ===Club=== Club Season League Australia Cup
